% Consumed by:
%   * anoretsCV.tex (via biblatex + biber)
%   * index.html    (via build_publications.py -- run by GitHub Actions)
%
% Custom (non-standard) fields used by the webpage build script:
%   pdf         relative URL to the paper PDF
%   code        relative URL to replication code archive
%   replication external URL to a replication package (e.g. Zenodo)
%   appendix    relative URL to a web/online appendix
%   extension   relative URL to an extension or companion paper
%   extlabel    label text for the extension link
%   note        extra free-form HTML appended after the citation
%   status      one of: published, forthcoming, working, old_working
%   sortdate    YYYY-MM string used to sort newest-first
%
% biblatex ignores unknown fields, so the CV is unaffected by these.
% --------------------------------------------------------------------


